<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-32-0799 </DOCNO><TEXT>In this article we analyse in some detail the theoretical and experimentalaspects of Compton FEL sources. The plan of the work is the following.In sect. 2 theory and experiments relevant to FEL sources are reviewed.Section 3 is devoted to the descriptions of electron accelerators moresuitable for FEL operation. Undulator-magnet and optical-resonator designand technology are discussed in sect. 4 and 5, respectively. Finallysect. 6 is devoted to conclusions and outlooks.</TEXT></DOC>